COVID-19 really has negative effect on the overall GDP of Nigeria.
States with high population have high number of confirmed cases.
Lagos state and Abuja are the states with highest number of confirmed cases and highest number of death. Kogi state has the lowest number of confirmed case.
The list of the first five states most affected by budget reduction due to covid-19 are: Cross-river , Lagos ,Akwa Ibom , Rivers and Ogun State

